{"tid":1065362,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩由大公司轉左去細公司，老闆痴q線","createTime":"2019-03-17T07:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T02:08:05.000Z","uid":226082,"like":83,"dislike":570,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"29cda69d42d2051a0ff1d7323d4447843ddb99a3","tid":1065362,"uid":226082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:51:58.000Z","msg":"本身係大公司做開，年年底薪加3%<br />\n雖然番得開心，但做左幾年就發現underpaid 左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新年前有公司聯絡我<br />\n話有細公司急請我個position<br />\n可以加我15k，大假都多幾日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然咩都唔諗即轉啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知返左公司3日<br />\n發現老闆做埋唔少仆街野<br />\n直頭係害人果隻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n好迷茫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正評：繼續做, 避開唔參與拒做的仆街野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負評：食回頭草返舊公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e65456d76e41ee80f3d0b384cc766d6d0f5b0373","tid":1065362,"uid":176601,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:55:15.000Z","msg":"可能揾你做替死鬼"},{"pid":"d6efa9b1acdc63c5af595019e93487835fc6cd92","tid":1065362,"uid":53062,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:55:38.000Z","msg":"有冇例子"},{"pid":"1884f447ee1b8111f43404028da8268ac6317792","tid":1065362,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":43,"score":-41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-17T07:57:05.000Z",